Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.18,0:02:13.19,ep-title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2100,0)\be1}A Sea of Writings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginko. It's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How's your work?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Same old.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How's Tanyuu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Same old as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.77,0:02:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She was writing earlier; she's resting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to the archives again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:02:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to read?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I read mostly everything up to the last generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then everything from Tanyuu's generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They're on the shelves over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:03:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Give me your tobacco.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't smoke it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take any risks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You must not forget that these texts
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,aren't just treatment references.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,these texts are no doubt confidential.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just the content,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but even the very reason for its existence is secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Foreword:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Birth of the fourth Karibusa Family scribe Tanyuu
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}by Karibusa Family Mushi-shi Minai Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The black birth mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She is the fourth scribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanyuu-ojousan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, return to your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go play outside too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to keep studying how to read and write?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't my legs move?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you would understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I will explain everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The mark on your leg comes from\Nwhen a Mushi was contained.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My ancestors contained a forbidden\NMushi in your ancestor's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Forbidden?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,By nature, plants and animals\Nexist in harmony with Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Where plants and animals thrive, Mushi also thrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Where plants and animals die, Mushi also die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But when plants, animals and Mushi declined\Nin a great disaster long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,an anomalous Mushi came to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and tried to destroy all other life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What sort of Mushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Its appearance, its shape, how it was contained...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,not a single record has been found.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What has been passed down in my lineage...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:07:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,is that the body of your ancestor who contained\Nthe Mushi was covered in black.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mushi survived in her body,\Nbut she died after giving birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Every few generations since then in the Karibusa family,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,a child is born with a black mark on part of their body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it still living in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I going to die too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I am here so that you will not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You are given the ability to quell the Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I will assist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're a better writer,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,come with me to my country home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:08:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There we will drive the forbidden Mushi underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the mark on your body will be\Ngone and you will be able to walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That is how three of your ancestors\Nso far have slowly quelled it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss, we have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That was an old dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surprised by the remedy that Tama taught me then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am going to tell you a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:09:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Write it down on paper later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All the stories that Tama told me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,were stories of Mushi that she'd defeated\Nwhen she was a Mushi-shi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They were true stories that seemed\Nalmost like fairy tales.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The grandiose stories she told intensely,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the sad stories she told in candlelight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Distant lands, foreign people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I was always captivated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I write them on paper, excruciating\Npain runs through the mark on my foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are the Mushi coming out of my body?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The tales of the Mushi being defeated\Nare the bane of this Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It is painful but please bear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:10:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You were forced to become a Mushi-shi\Nfor my sake, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it painful?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't it anger you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've forgotten all such things when I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I am grateful now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.81,0:10:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It was when Tama ran out of stories...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.66,0:10:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and called in other Mushi-shi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that I began to realize how much effort\Nshe made to make it easier for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And to exterminate the pest,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:11:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I spread this predacious Mushi all over the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Within a month, the pests were gone without a trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, when that was done,\NI exterminated this Mushi as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.61,0:11:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be good for it to become too dominant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All of the stories I'd heard until then\Nwere in essence all about killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The pain in my leg came to bring pain to my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Arrogance towards the minute and inferior life forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Murder brought forth by baseless fear of the paranormal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Those notions became more than noticeable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it necessary to kill them, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:12:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,With all due respect, I believe you could only\Nspeak of it if you've dealt with Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.37,0:12:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But there wasn't anything I could do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If only my legs would move.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Say there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the daughter of the Karibusa family?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thought so. There aren't any other homes around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so this must be that black birth mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a Mushi-shi too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.07,0:12:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're collecting Mushi stories, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard I'd be allowed to browse the\NKaribusa Archives if I helped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, leave please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of hearing about killing Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:12:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How about stories about {\i1}not{\i0} killing them then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I think I have more of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That wouldn't do me any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start with the story about\Nthe skin mole-eating Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Moles?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,About that Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not supposed to let you in\Nwithout Tama's permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But I doubt she'd want to hire a Mushi-shi like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just handle it carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mushi are inside the text.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:14:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I heard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The forbidden Mushi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.28,0:14:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, this is a Mushi-shi's gold chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's all just a catalog of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hear more about animals\Nand Mushi living together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll persuade Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you please come to talk again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.85,0:14:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Gladly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginko is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring him in, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimi eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit, here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The text's falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Has it awakened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Otama-san, the Shimi's eating the paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to break the seals.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Parts of the seals have been broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They are headed your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, there's no getting out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.03,0:16:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No kidding, you'd never think they were\Nconcealed for hundreds of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm talking about you, Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't seem worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you put them back?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can contain Mushi too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.34,0:16:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The text stopped moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There's special glue on the walls\Nand ceiling of this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:16:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Volume 1853.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapter one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapter two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You have it all memorized?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Paper decays after a while whether\Nor not there's any Shimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.48,0:17:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So the text has to be transcribed little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Though it wouldn't suffice to just copy it normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the technique that's been\Npassed down in my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Those Shimi are her beloved pets.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I like them, they're cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think they've overbred?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. So long as I do the transcription properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a dangerous game.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't mess up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my task.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a girl living and drowning in a sea of words.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We should call it a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even half of it could go towards\Ncontaining the Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.71,0:18:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you tired? You haven't slept.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginko, stay here until I'm done please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a girl whose body is eaten away by Mushi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,who appreciates Mushi and who contains Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Has she finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Blanket, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.14,0:20:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you take me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.91,0:20:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder when I'll be able to move these legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The mark's slowly going away, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.64,0:20:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Very slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.22,0:20:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't get rid of it by the time I die,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.85,0:20:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the burden will eventually go to my descendants.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:21:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as it has until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it won't end at my generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.92,0:21:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do when your leg heals?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to travel with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see the Mushi that you've\Nbeen telling me about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.19,0:21:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.69,0:21:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be an old lady by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.54,0:21:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.54,0:21:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.92,0:22:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But only if I survive until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.84,0:22:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You better live.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.47,0:22:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, I might get eaten by a Mushi tomorrow even.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.89,0:22:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You better live anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.90,0:22:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.73,0:22:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine.
